title: TRANSFILM 2 1/2 GAL ANTI-TRANSPIRANT
description: Winter can suck the moisture right out of turf and plants. But you can provide winter protection for plants with TransFilm Anti-Transpirant. An emulsion of polyethylenes-polyterpenes, TransFilm coats leaf surfaces with a clear, glossy film that provides a water-impermeable layer to protect the plant and decrease the rate of transpiration.
